axies with blue or green optical colors. Consequently, while\nAGN activity and star formation appear to be globally correlated, we do not\nfind evidence that the presence of an AGN is related to the quenching of star\nformation or the color transformation of galaxies.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 21 Jul 2011 20:00:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 26 Jul 2011 20:37:34 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 4 Feb 2012 02:36:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
