et unknown process which efficiently heats or expels gas at\nhigh redshifts.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2011 06:02:19 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 20 Jan 2012 02:40:43 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-05-28"}
