 neutrino flux from the decay of different particles (muon, pion, neutron\nand kaon) may vary and they would also be reflected on the neutrino flavour\nratios.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 22 Jul 2011 11:21:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sun, 20 Nov 2011 09:28:56 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sun, 27 May 2012 03:52:49 GMT"}],"update_date":"2012-06-29"}
